So, `P.liftContext lens` has:
- `input` is `fun x => ⟨P.input (lens.proj x.2.1), x⟩`
- `sendMessage` is `fun i' x => ...`
- `receiveChallenge` is `fun i' x => ...`
- `output` is `fun x => ...`

When we call `processRound i resultRound`:
- `resultRound` is `⟨transcript, state⟩` where `state` is `P.PrvState i × OuterStmtIn × OuterWitIn`
